OL,3,CRent caps and protection from
OL,4,Cunreasonable evictions proposed in law
OL,6,FTenants in could be given more
OL,7,Fprotection if a new housing law is
OL,8,Fpassed by the States.
OL,10,FThe legislation would limit rent rises
OL,11,Fto once a year with a minimum notice
OL,12,Fperiod before the higher rate is
OL,13,Fbrought in and it would guard against
OL,14,F"excessive" increases.
OL,16,FUnder the proposed changes,
OL,17,F"inappropriate fees and charges" would
OL,18,Fbe banned with an appeals process for
OL,19,Flandlords and tenants, plus penalties
OL,20,Fif people do not comply.
