OL,6,FA new type of tenancy has been
OL,7,Fsuggested which would offer an initial
OL,8,Ffixed-term contract with extended
OL,9,Fminimum notice periods for long-
OL,10,Fstanding renters.
OL,12,FLandlords would however be able to
OL,13,Ftake swifter action against tenants in
OL,14,Fserious breach of their agreement with
OL,15,Fa set of reasons included in the law
OL,16,Fto allow properties to be reclaimed.
