OL,6,FHousing Minister Sam Mezec is bringing
OL,7,Fforward the changes and says: "I want
OL,8,Ftenants to feel like they have
OL,9,Fsecurity in their homes, in their
OL,10,Flives, to know that if they have
OL,11,Fproblems with the property they aren't
OL,12,Fgoing to get punished for it and to
OL,13,Fknow when there are unfair and
OL,14,Funjustifiable rental suggestions, they
OL,15,Fwill have the power to stand up to
OL,16,Fthemselves.
