OL,6,F"Delivering greater protections for
OL,7,Ftenants, whilst balancing this against
OL,8,Fthe rights of landlords, within a
OL,9,Fmodern and fit-for-purpose framework,
OL,10,Fwill go a huge way to alleviating this
OL,11,Faspect of the housing crisis."
OL,13,FHe believes the current rules are out
OL,14,Fof date and hopes these proposals
OL,15,Fcould be approved by politicians and
OL,16,Fcome into law by 2025.
OL,18,FOne Jersey tenant told ITV News that
OL,19,Fher landlord said he would increase
OL,20,Fher rent within two months of moving
