OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously, she explains:
OL,7,F"Everyone in my position who is
OL,8,Funqualified has limited options so
OL,9,Fwhen you do find something that is in
OL,10,Fyour budget, which is rare, you don't
OL,11,Fwant to make a fuss because you don't
OL,12,Fwant to get booted out.
OL,14,F"There are so many rules so when you
OL,15,Fdon't have somewhere to live, you
OL,16,Freally don't have somewhere to live."
